name: Thurston County Public Health Medical Reserve Corp
address: Capital Mall - 625 Black Lake Boulevard Southwest, Olympia WA, 98502
vaccines: Janssen COVID-19 Vaccine, Moderna COVID-19 Vaccine
info: This is a single-dose Johnson & Johnson clinic being held at Capital Mall, 625 Black Lake Blvd SW, Olympia WA, 98502 for anyone age 18 and older from 12pm until mall closing. We will be located inside the mall, closest to the Sephora end of the mall and next to the Buckle store.
